lead_paragraph: Former No. 1 Caroline Wozniacki won her appeal Thursday for a spot in the tennis tournament at the Rio de Janeiro Olympics, while 14-time major champion Rafael Nadal's status is still up in the air.

headline.print_headline: Denmark's Wozniacki Wins Appeal to Participate in Rio Games
